  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAnnotationParser  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractParser
    Parses the content of the result xml generated by a annotation run.
    CRAFTParser
    This class parses the CRAFT goldstandard so it may be used with the extracted annotations lists from the extractor software tested and work as a reference point.
    CRAFTParserTest  
    CTakesParser
    First implementation for the test of the cTakes extractor.
    CTakesParserTest
    This test class also tests the methods provided by the abstract class.
    MetaMapParser
    Parses the result files returned by MetaMap.
    MetamapParserTest2
    This test class also tests the methods provided by the abstract class.
    ParserFactory
    This factory "produces" various extractor and goldstandard parsers to extract the annotations from the result files of an extractor run on an biomedical text.
    ParserHelper
    Contains some delegate methods that are useful for
    the parsing process.
    ParserHelperTest  
    QuickUmlsParser
    Parses the result files returned by the QuickUMLS extractor.
